classDiagram
    %% PawPal+ current design (notes-as-tasks). Update as the implementation evolves.

    class Pet {
        +str name
        +str species
        +str breed
        +int age_years
        +list~str~ notes
        +add_note(text) None
        +edit_note(index, new_text) None
        +remove_note(index) None
        +update_info(**fields) None
    }

    class Owner {
        +str name
        +list~Pet~ pets
        +int daily_minutes_available
        +dict preferences
        +add_pet(pet) None
        +update_info(**fields) None
    }

    class Task {
        +str title
        +str priority
        +str start
        +str end
        +int duration_minutes
        +str pet_name
        +str raw
    }

    class Scheduler {
        +Owner owner
        +tasks() list~Task~
        +sort_tasks(tasks) list~Task~
        +build_plan() Plan
    }

    class Plan {
        +list scheduled
        +list skipped
        +int total_minutes_used
        +int day_budget
        +render() list
        +explain() str
    }

    Owner "1" --> "*" Pet : has
    Scheduler --> Owner : uses
    Scheduler ..> Task : produces
    Scheduler --> Plan : produces
